        </div>
        
        <div class="scenario-card">
          <h3>Home Renovations</h3>
          <p>Major renovations, especially to basements or foundations, can change radon levels in your home.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="scenario-card">
          <h3>Every 2 Years</h3>
          <p>Even if previous tests showed safe levels, radon can change over time due to settling, weather, and home modifications.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="scenario-card">
          <h3>After Mitigation</h3>
